<div class="container-fluid">
  <div class="row" style="margin-top: 5em; margin-left: 5em">
    <div class="col-md-4">
      <div class="welcome-text">
        <h1>
          THE BEST <br />
          <div class="italien">ITALIAN</div>
          COFFEE
        </h1>
        <div class="text-brown">
          Welcome to CafeAroma. We are <br />
          passionate about coffee and offer <br />
          you the finest coffee products of <br />
          the highest quality. Our company <br />
          was born from our love for the <br />
          bean, and we want to share this <br />
          passion with you.
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="buttons" style="margin-top: 1em">
        <% if(req.me) { %>
        <a href="/shop" class="brown-button">BUY </a>
        <% } else { %>
        <a href="/login" class="brown-button">BUY </a>
        <% } %>

        <a href="/cafe" class="brown-button">VIEW MORE</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="col-md-5">
      <img class="HomePic" , alt="Expresso" src="/images/expresso.png" />
    </div>

    <div class="col-md-3">
      <div
        class="text-brown"
        style="
          margin-top: 5em;
          margin-right: 2em;
          font-weight: 300;
          font-size: 20px;
        "
      >
        CafeAroma is more than a brand; it's a commitment to sharing the
        richness of this passion with you.We look forward to enhancing your
        coffee experience and being part of your coffee journey. Browse through
        our products, read our menu, and feel free to contact us if you have any
        questions. Thank you for choosing
      </div>
      <div class="cafearoma">CafeAroma</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row" style="margin-top: 10em">
    <div class="col-md-6" style="margin-left: 2em">
      <div class="Bold-Title">
        But first.. Cafe
        <img
          src="/images/logoCute.png"
          style="margin-left: 0.1em; margin-bottom: 1em"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="cafe-text" style="margin-top: -1em">
        Explore various coffee preparations, from the rich and creamy cappuccino
        to the robust and energizing macchiato.We believe that understanding the
        art of coffee preparation enhances the overall coffee experience. Our
        range includes a wide selection of coffee beans from different regions
        of the world, carefully roasted to preserve the full flavor aromatic
        essence, ranging from the timeless classic of Arabica to the allure of
        exotic varieties, ensuring a coffee to suit every taste.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div
    class="row justify-content-end"
    style="margin-top: 10em; margin-right: 5em"
  >
    <div class="col-md-8" style="margin-top: 10em">
      <div class="cafe-text">
        Our commitment extends beyond providing the finest coffee; our website
        is a valuable resource offering <br />
        insightful articles and tips on everything coffee-related. Immerse
        yourself in our expertise,<br />
        and feel free to reach out with any questions. We take pride in our
        expertise and wish to share our knowledge with you.
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="col-md-4">
      <div class="Bold-Title" style="text-align: center">
        What's your aestehtic?
      </div>

      <div id="hero-carousel" class="carousel slide" data-bs-ride="carousel">
        <div class="carousel-inner">
          <div class="carousel-item active c-item">
            <img
              class="d-block w-100"
              src="/images/picLeft.png"
              alt="First slide"
            />
          </div>

          <div class="carousel-item c-item">
            <img
              class="d-block w-100"
              src="/images/picright.png"
              alt="second slide"
            />
          </div>
        </div>

        <button
          class="carousel-control-prev"
          type="button"
          data-bs-target="#hero-carousel"
          data-bs-slide="prev"
        >
          <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="visually-hidden">Previous</span>
        </button>
        <button
          class="carousel-control-next"
          type="button"
          data-bs-target="#hero-carousel"
          data-bs-slide="next"
        >
          <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="visually-hidden">Next</span>
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
